[Script]
# > 髦ｿ驥御ｺ醍尨遲ｾ蛻ｰ
https://auth.alipan.com/v2/account/token
髦ｿ驥御ｺ醍尨遲ｾ蛻ｰcookie = requires-body=1,type=http-response,pattern=https:¥/¥/auth.(aliyundrive|alipan).com¥/v2¥/account¥/token,script-path=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lowking/Scripts/master/ali/aliYunPanCheckIn.js
髦ｿ驥御ｺ醍尨遲ｾ蛻ｰ = type=cron,cronexp="0 10 0 * * ?",wake-system=1,script-path=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lowking/Scripts/master/ali/aliYunPanCheckIn.js

[MITM]
hostname = %APPEND% auth.alipan.com